Main article detailing arbitrage opportunity:
https://messari.io/article/arbitraging-uniswap-and-sushiswap-in-node-js

The link details how to implement the ideas. 

A guide is given for building a bot that will
execute the trades on Uniswap and Sushiswap.

The business logic for this bot will be:
Monitor latest prices on Uniswap and SushiSwap
Decide whether to trade
Execute trade

Uniswap:
https://uniswap.org/
Sushiswap:
https://sushi.com/
